    "Such expansion would not only validate the generalizability of the findings but also open new avenues for applying WCET estimation in diverse real-world contexts, from autonomous vehicles to critical infrastructure monitoring.In addition, although we applied our method in robotic systems, our approach can also be applied to other domains, such as embedded systems.",
    "Since our approach is based on a black-box model, it can be adapted to different systems as long as the input format is known.",
    "This flexibility allows for broader applicability across various real-time systems that require accurate WCET estimation.• Contributions to Real-Time Systems Reliability: The implications of this research extend into the broader realm of enhancing the reliability and performance of real-time systems.",
    "By providing a foundation for WCET estimation, the findings contribute towards the development of systems that are not only efficient and responsive but also robust against operational uncertainties.",
